title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 8/31 - 11 Reasons, John Bonnes
description: The Vikings take on the Packers in 11 days, so PA & Nordo open the show giving you 11 reasons why the Vikings will win the season opener.  John Bonnes joins the show to discuss the Twins winning streak, playoff chances, & more!
